We expand
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

 in the piecewise constant functions and 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x)=\sum_{i=1}^{N-1}u_{i}\psi_{i}(x)
\]

\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

